      <scopecontent encodinganalog="MARC 520">
         <head id="a3">COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
         <p>Records of the Reformed Church of Interlaken, New York, a Dutch Reformed church
            (formerly the Reformed Dutch Church of Farmerville, New York), including minutes,
            membership lists, and records of baptisms and marriages.</p>
      </scopecontent>
